Category:  General  Topic:  follow



When you follow someone, you will attempt to follow them where ever they
go.  Whoever you follow can group you if they wish.  

syntax:  follow		Makes you follow yourself.
	 follow Grock	You now follow Grock.

See Also:  group, ungroup, order, gs

Note:  If you stop following a leader of a group, then you are automatically
       removed from the group.
